- Come and try.

354
00:26:00,390 --> 00:26:00,990
Give it a try.

355
00:26:00,990 --> 00:26:01,590
Okay, I'll try.

356
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:02,110
Help him up.

357
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:02,688
Come on.

358
