Off you go.

359
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:05,910
Okay, okay.

360
00:26:05,910 --> 00:26:07,350
You'd hold him, and I'll go over there.

361
00:26:08,150 --> 00:26:08,800
Come on.

362
00:26:12,870 --> 00:26:15,470
Okay, I'll clear the way.

